canonical:
  title: 風荷
  author: 崔瀣
  language: lzh
  text: 淸晨纔罷浴臨鏡力不持天然無限美揔在未粧時
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 風荷
  author: 崔瀣
  language: lzh
  text: 淸晨纔罷浴。臨鏡力不持。天然無限美。揔在未粧時。
korean:
  title: 풍하
  author: 최해
  language: kor
  text: |-
    맑은 새벽에 겨우 목욕을 마치고
    거울 앞에서 힘을 가누지 못하네
    천연의 무한한 아름다움이란
    전혀 단장하기 전에 있구나
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0220_010_0350&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: Wind-Touched Lotus
  author: Choe Hae
  language: eng
  text: |-
    At dawn, having just finished bathing,
    Before the mirror, I cannot hold myself steady—
    Such infinite natural beauty,
    Exists entirely before any adornment.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: The title 'Wind-Touched Lotus' (風荷) evokes both the delicate beauty of lotus flowers swayed by wind and the subject's ethereal grace. The poem celebrates unadorned beauty in its most genuine form.
